000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講得冇錯</blockquote><br />\n我堅持等佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐵柱磨成針！但重點要搵到佢，朋友再黎過可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5923f9fa7d57b1cb42085b5c0dd92715d823e2a","tid":514993,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係<br />\n女仔對你有感情就咩都可以<br />\n冇就好絕情</blockquote><br />\n女仔絕情只需3個鐘，成個世界就變晒。好空虛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係被拋棄嗰個"},{"pid":"dd6024e668f491c88657599b6d88a159faeea212","tid":514993,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講得冇錯</blockquote><br />\n我堅持等佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐵柱磨成針！但重點要搵到佢，朋友再黎過可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但人地永遠唔知道你等"},{"pid":"f8c67654b0b2d04e99c23204c5742d3142671983","tid":514993,"uid":143307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講得冇錯</blockquote><br />\n我堅持等佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐵柱磨成針！但重點要搵到佢，朋友再黎過可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但人地永遠唔知道你等</blockquote><br />\n你要明白<br />\n其實 真係返唔轉頭<br />\n有好多嘢真係過咗就返唔到<br />\n好似佢咁 曾經好愛 然後唔愛 跟第二個<br />\n好多事<br />\n係會變<br />\n<br />\n所以我仲還記得佢講<br />\n已經冇可能再返都過去<br />\n感情冇就係冇"},{"pid":"046737a9a13d32dd8302d705a558246a1fa67561","tid":514993,"uid":164858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係<br />\n女仔對你有感情就咩都可以<br />\n冇就好絕情</blockquote><br />\n女仔絕情只需3個鐘，成個世界就變晒。好空虛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係被拋棄嗰個</blockquote><br />\n大家同一情況...我想搵佢但一d方法都無！又唔會去佢屋企/公司樓下等佢，我仲有男人應有既風度..."},{"pid":"d1124017d4652c47dfb4ada3758a540dda7f701c","tid":514993,"uid":164858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講得冇錯</blockquote><br />\n我堅持等佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐵柱磨成針！但重點要搵到佢，朋友再黎過可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但人地永遠唔知道你等</blockquote><br />\n佢封鎖晒...我知道緣份將我地拉得埋！有緣一定會再相見。睇黎要出多d街！見到咩野當時運高<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8a5af1e7ddbc0f818c857a3df1eac20f4a32da","tid":514993,"uid":164858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講得冇錯</blockquote><br />\n我堅持等佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐵柱磨成針！但重點要搵到佢，朋友再黎過可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但人地永遠唔知道你等</blockquote><br />\n你要明白<br />\n其實 真係返唔轉頭<br />\n有好多嘢真係過咗就返唔到<br />\n好似佢咁 曾經好愛 然後唔愛 跟第二個<br />\n好多事<br />\n係會變<br />\n<br />\n所以我仲還記得佢講<br />\n已經冇可能再返都過去<br />\n感情冇就係冇</blockquote><br />\n我感覺好似空白左段回憶"},{"pid":"2b2505c0be7d53ab77b2ec1c602c5c8055ae23df","tid":514993,"uid":60787,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"好男人係情場冇市場嘅<br />\n所有女都係貪新鮮鍾意玩愛刺激<br />\n試問咩都遵規道舉，對佢千依百順嘅好男人又點會俾到Feel班女？<br />\n只有到班女人老珠黃玩夠想生仔<br />\n咪會搵好男人埋單囉"},{"pid":"2a255bb39f98541cd3f5b7000145e2952afadac6","tid":514993,"uid":162441,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"女人愈好，男仔愈唔愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471744838803ff020e134be3691e7fe330a2c204","tid":514993,"uid":52041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3611d485fcd4fa0ece42e4ba0d891af55b1d3bb1","tid":514993,"uid":164858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"